  ". Local playback pauses when casting starts.": "。投射开始时，本地播放会暂停。",
  "Apps and DLNA: ECHO is a standard UPnP AV (DLNA MediaRenderer). Any app that can cast to a TV/speaker over DLNA and sends a playable HTTP(S) stream can usually connect; device names and metadata vary by app. QQ Music and some others on Android/iOS support DLNA—check each app’s help. Spotify desktop normally uses Spotify Connect or system Bluetooth/speakers, not DLNA; if a build offers DLNA or a third-party bridge, try selecting this PC from the device list.": "应用程序和 DLNA：ECHO 是标准 UPnP AV (DLNA MediaRenderer)。任何可以通过 DLNA 投射到电视/扬声器并发送可播放的 HTTP(S) 流的应用程序通常都可以连接；设备名称和元数据因应用程序而异。 QQ 音乐和 Android/iOS 上的其他一些应用程序支持 DLNA — 查看每个应用程序的帮助。 Spotify 桌面通常使用 Spotify Connect 或系统蓝牙/扬声器，而不是 DLNA；如果版本提供 DLNA 或第三方桥接器，请尝试从设备列表中选择此电脑。",
  "NetEase Cloud Music: Enable “Connect DLNA devices” in settings; on the player screen open Devices / Cast and pick this device (same name as above). If it does not appear: confirm the LAN IP shown below is on the same subnet as your phone (wrong NIC or VPN is common); set env ECHOES_DLNA_IP to this PC’s Wi‑Fi IPv4 and check Windows Firewall for this app and UDP 1900. If playback fails, the URL may be encrypted—cast from inside the official app and keep it updated.": "网易云音乐：在设置中启用“连接DLNA设备”；在播放器屏幕上打开“设备/投射”并选择此设备（与上面的名称相同）。如果没有出现：确认如下所示的LAN IP与您的手机在同一子网中（常见的是错误的网卡或VPN）；将 env ECHOES_DLNA_IP 设置为此电脑的 Wi-Fi IPv4，并检查此应用程序的 Windows 防火墙和 UDP 1900。如果播放失败，则 URL 可能已加密 - 从官方应用程序内部投射并保持更新。",
